pricing_analysis.pricing_trend: Aggressive price compression and a push for performance-per-dollar. Output costs consistently remain 3-5x higher than input costs. Subscription models (e.g., ChatGPT Plus, Claude Pro, AI Premium) at $20/month have become the standard for consumer access to top-tier models. A new tier of highly capable, ultra-low-cost 'fast' models (e.g., Gemini Flash, Claude Haiku) is emerging for high-volume, less-complex tasks.
